=== Nausea
<subsec:nausea>

*Clinical Presentation.*

    - Chronic or recurrent nausea
    - Nausea triggered by exertion, movement, or sensory stimulation
    - Medication-induced nausea (many ME/CFS patients have heightened sensitivity)
    - Early satiety (feeling full quickly)
    - Food aversions
